{"tid":291800,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"聽Bon Iver既/聽英文cover既入黎","createTime":"2017-06-21T00:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T16:15:17.000Z","uid":78460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a01fe35ba273428cbe06d3afde2b2ad8619dc5c","tid":291800,"uid":78460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"到宜家都好少冇人開過Bon Iver既post咁我黎啦<br />\nBon Iver由唱作既Justin Vernon同其他樂手組成 2008年失戀閉關寫左d歌出左隻碟&quot;For Emma, Forever Ago&quot; 主要為acoustic既folk music為主 當中佢有力既假音最為代表性 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Dz5s5C6sAt0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDz5s5C6sAt0&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3adfc565\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Dz5s5C6sAt0</a><br />\n三年後2011年又出左Alblum &quot;Bon Iver, Bon Iver&quot; 呢隻碟明顯聽得出Justin Vernon既音樂方向開始越黎越廣 作曲同編曲方面都比較講究同複雜 特別係樂器既配搭 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TWcyIpul8OE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTWcyIpul8OE&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a8fcf554\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TWcyIpul8OE</a>"},{"pid":"6c3d225ce6ba73416bbc26cf6dd5fb02c7ade301","tid":291800,"uid":78460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:48:49.000Z","msg":"然後事隔五年後2016 Bon Iver又以新既音樂重現樂壇 就算忠實既fans可能都會一時適應唔到 就由唱片既曲目一堆既怪碼已經略略估到 Bon Iver新既專輯作曲方面唔再停留響主流既verse chorus verse chorus chorus既格式 而編曲入面用左好多sampling 加上最突出既 一定係聲 Justin今次用左一個特別為佢設計既vocoder 令佢唱既時候會主動幫佢和音 或者改變聲線 呢個approach更加用左落唔少樂器例如saxophone度 但係響咁多改變之後 仍然會聽到有folk既底元素 仲有唔少得既就係Vernon既靚歌詞 同埋就係俾CD版仲精彩既Live performance<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6C5sB6AqJkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6C5sB6AqJkM&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=a2f5d526\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6C5sB6AqJkM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9utVR5Q67_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9utVR5Q67_k&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=8692896a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9utVR5Q67_k</a><br />\n仍然保留住folk味<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wHtJJm93ey8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwHtJJm93ey8&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=e775fc93\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wHtJJm93ey8</a><br />\n聽完CD版再聽Live真係冇得頂"},{"pid":"fc6186b3c3296f016a8fea0cd090a2aff03f9dda","tid":291800,"uid":78460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T00:50:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有興趣就聽埋我個cover</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/user-773160948/22-over-sn-bon-ivercover\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Fuser-773160948%2F22-over-sn-bon-ivercover&d=CpdBlFin1w%2F29JcLDvXN%2B0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=fc0d1d76\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/user-773160948/22-over-sn-bon-ivercover</a>"},{"pid":"a0f485c91d5024c4e6e795b6b9fa93405fba478a","tid":291800,"uid":58352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:15:17.000Z","msg":"佢地d live 真係不得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}